    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since the moment I got it\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like a member of the family. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There\u2019s a tiny, tiny mark on the rear wheel that you\u2019d have to squint to even see, but otherwise, she\u2019s pure perfection. I\u2019m only selling to make some room in the garage for a new project, so I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
